            <title>[FLINK-6509] TestingListener might miss JobLeader notifications</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-6509</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;TestingListener&lt;/tt&gt; might miss JobLeader notifications because it does not perform the check under the lock. This should be changed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
